 "html": "<p>Dis asof die koue tot in mens se bene sny.  So wat n beter manier as om van binne warm te word.  Die sop is werklik maklik en gou om te maak.  Watter kaas jy bo-op krummel , is jou keuse.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>BENODIG:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 ui</li>\n<li>2 koppe brokkoli<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-005.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1704\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 005\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-005-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>60 ml botter</li>\n<li>1,5 liter aftreksel ( ek het 2 blokkies gevat en met 1,5liter kookwater gemeng)<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-015.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1707\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 015\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-015-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>2,5 ml neut<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-018.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1708\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 018\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-018-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>sout en peper na smaak</li>\n<li>250 ml room<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-026.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1711\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 026\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-026-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>1 driehoek bloukaas of cheddarkaas of feta ( hang af waarvan jy hou)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>sny die ui in ringetjies en braai in die botter</li>\n<li>was jou brokkoli af en breek in kleiner stukkies &#8211; roerbraai so bietjie saam met die uie<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1706\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 010\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-010-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>los die aftrekselblokkies op in die warmwater en gooi oor die brokkoli</li>\n<li>laat dit net stoom tot sag &#8211; nie papkook nie<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-020.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1709\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 020\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-020-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>geur met neut, sout en peper</li>\n<li>maak dit fyn in n voeselverwerker of met n blenderstok<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-021.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1710\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 021\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-021-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>gooi terug in die pot en roer die room deur<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-027.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1712\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 027\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-027-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>As jy dit bedien, krummel die kaas van jou keuse oor en geniet dit met n sny warm brood.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-034.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1714\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 034\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-034-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
